text: Demi-Leigh Tebow (n√©e Nel-Peters; born 28 June 1995) is a South African model and beauty pageant titleholder. She was crowned Miss Universe 2017. She was crowned Miss South Africa 2017, and is the second Miss Universe winner from South Africa. Nel-Peters married Tim Tebow on 20 January 2020. On January 14, 2025, they announced their pregnancy. ==References== Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:South African models Category:Miss Universe winners
